{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had-- I had disappeared to go and take my pneumothorax refill, and they thought maybe I was a spy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was when the Battle Of The Bulge, you know, the Americans came over in our section and all, and they thought, well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they checked me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and they never--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the Vosges Mountains.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Paris.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, in Paris.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to the hospital again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The day it finished, in the Vosges Mountains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A while, just a short while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Infantry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Alsatians, you know, a lot of people thought because they are part German anyway, you know, but they were quite aggressive against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They got a very bad press, I think, because I think the Alsatians were much maligned during the-- during the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People thought, well, maybe they-- and Colmar, for example, was a big, big center for the Nazis, and it was one of the worst fightings of the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a funny story about one of the-- about something in Colmar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a young kid, you know, very young, and his job was to go out and scrape the ice out from under the cars and all that, the command cars and the jeeps, of the German equivalent of the jeep.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was a businessman, too, so he would take the antifreeze, drain it out, and sell it, but he'd put water in in place of it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, when the machines would take off and then stop for an hour, it would freeze up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I suppose this man did-- this kid-- did more to frustrate the German army than--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "there were some terribly funny things that happened during the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
